<HEADLINE> Leno: L.A. Y2K Celebration a Flop  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Jay Leno, who pulled a switch to light up the Hollywood
sign during L.A.'s millennial celebration, says Tinseltown's big moment was a
flop.
</P>
