<HEADLINE> 'Clifford' Character Comes to PBS  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
    LOS ANGELES (AP) -- "Clifford the Big Red Dog," an animated program based on
the popular series of children's books, is coming to PBS in the fall.
</P>
<P>
	   The 40 half-hour episodes, airing Monday through Friday, will show
Clifford's world, including his loving human pal, Emily Elizabeth, and doggie
friends T-Bone and Cleo.
</P>
