Mitchell ("Keenan &AMP; Kel") as T-Bone, Grey DeLisle ("Caroline in the City") as
Emily Elizabeth and Cree Summer as Cleo.
</P>
<P>
	   In announcing the series Friday, PBS said it will emphasize good citizenship
and the importance of community. "Clifford" is designed for 3- to-7-year-old
children.
